messages.content: What is ComfyUI_Segment_Mask and where is it from?

ComfyUI_Segment_Mask is a ComfyUI version of the original project at https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything. It is a version of the Segment Anything Model, which is designed to segment any image into regions with a simple and controllable interface. The specific implementation details can be found at the provided link.
